reviewText: A fascinating and funny production -- and great gymnastics.  A big hit!

I think i recorded this competition off tv and i loved it more than anything! i watched it everday because it was so entertaining and fun! unfortunately my tape got lost and I have been desperately searching for it once again. If anyone can make me a copy, please contact me at [...]. Thank you so much and in the subject put rock n roll gymnastics!

This has got to be the best gymnastics video (and competition) you will find. Extremely entertaining. A lot of the performances had me laughing even after it was over, and a lot of them made me dance and do gymnastics right there in my family room. Seriously, a GREAT video.
